xt"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","isActive":true},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"atoll: the inner island would be one ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true},{"text":" object, while the surrounding","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"group of disconnected but related buildings.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMultiPolygon","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"symbol"}}}